summary: Modern Thanksgiving Day AU where the Starks and the Baratheons are celebrating together in some big fancy cabin. Arya is having...
body:
Modern Thanksgiving Day AU where the Starks and the Baratheons are celebrating together in some big fancy cabin. Arya is having it out with Joffrey because he’s being an elitist dick, Robert is drunk and keeps calling Arya Lyanna and Gendry being like fuck you because he has absolutely no time for his sperm donor’s fake happy family bullshit.

Some fun extra things:

- Jon brings Ygritte home for the first time.

- Sansa just wants everything to be nice and copes by eating all the lemon cakes.

- Shaggydog probably knocks something over and eats the whole turkey. Rickon thinks it’s hilarious.

- Bran keeps trying to slip out so he can go climb trees in the forest.

- Theon’s pissed that there’s no one in the area on Tinder to swipe right.

- Robb wishes they’d all just stayed in Winterfell.

- Arya probably tries to break Joffrey’s nose.

- Gendry definitely tells Robert to fuck off.

tags: I headcanon that Arya and Dany are best friends
summary:
Arrested For...
Arya: *Public intoxication, public indecency, and theft*
Dany, come to bail out her best friend: Do you want to...
body:
Arrested For…

Arya: *Public intoxication, public indecency, and theft*

Dany, come to bail out her best friend: Do you want to tell me what happened or am I supposed to guess?

Arya: I didn’t do anything!

Dany: *slamming hand down* Bullshit!

Arya: In my defense, how was I supposed to know there was actually someone in that police car?

Dany: What does that MEAN?

Arya: So Gendry and I were hanging out-

Dany: Say no more

Arya: Do you want to know or not?!

Dany: *nodding*

Arya: We decided to go to a museum and they had an event with an open bar

Dany: *sits down with a heavy sigh*

Arya: I may have gotten into my cups

Dany: May?

Arya: And there was a sword on display that I thought was cool

Dany: Arya, you didn’t

Arya: I did

Dany: Wait, how does the indecency and police car come into this?

Arya: *blushing* Um, so Gendry and I make off with the sword and we’re stumbling through the streets and he was talking about how awesome I would look riding a wolf into battle with the sword

Dany: And?

Arya: We were in an empty street, or what I thought was an empty street and-

Dany: *slow realization* Did you have sex on a police car

Arya: Is that respect I detect?

summary: Is it me or is gendrya in the books totally one sided?
question: Is it me or is gendrya in the books totally one sided?
answer:
I don’t think it’s one-sided. 

I just think that GRRM is (rightfully) delaying a romance with Arya and a love interest 5 years her senior, since she was only 9-10 when they met. 

I expect Gendrya to be romantic once Arya’s flowered.

summary: Just a little GOT Haiku’s
title: Just a little GOT Haiku’s
body:
So, a not so know fact about me….I write Haiku’s. I have been writing Haiku’s since I was in high school and even have a journal full of them. Obviously, life happens and I stopped for a while. I picked back up after I was in a really no so good place in my life. I have written a few for Game of Thrones. I will post a couple about GOT, but I will also post some to boost morale. Here are few, and I hope you enjoy!

P.S.

The first one is not one I wrote. I don’t know who did, but I feel like I should mention that I did not write it. I chose it though, because it reminds me of a certain character in GOT.

1)      An ocean voyage

As waves break over the bow

The sea welcomes her

2)      Stubborn, yes they are

Always fighting, arguing

Yet, loving each other

3)      Grey eyes meet blue eyes

The Storm and Ocean collide

But break apart suddenly

4)      Banging the hammer

Hot steel bending to his will

The forge is his home

5)      A girl is No One

And a girl is a Lone Wolf

But a Bull follows

Let me know what you think! If you want more, I will write more! Ask me what you want to read and I will try to make it happen!

summary: i am deadset working on a fic where dany, arya, missandei, yara, brienne and literally any other woman get shit done. it’s...
body:
i am deadset working on a fic where dany, arya, missandei, yara, brienne and literally any other woman get shit done. it’s really not canon but I guess at the start it is. so basically sansa will play tyrion like really play him, arya will play the game of faces and turn into a different person or two, dany and jon are actually gonna be fully in love and a betrothal will be set in place in mutual agreement of sansa and arya and jon. dany is willing to give bran the north and shes planning on making sansa her new hand and arya her mistress of whispers and laws. they work together to come up with a plan to take down cersei. their armies heal and so does rhaegal. instead of reconvening on dragonstone they head to storms end instead, swiftly and without much notice. tyrion and varys are still trying to give her shitty advice and sansa shuts them down any chance she gets. dany has plans for them. tyrion has told cersei they’d be heading to dragonstone (he didn’t know they’d be going to stormsend) so when eurons fleet shows up and there’s no one there they’re all like wtf and then boom drogon and rhaegal burn the fleet and they take euron as a prisoner. yara later executes him. arya and gendry get to know the stormlands and the people they’ll be ruling over when this war is over. sansa gets tyrion to spill his whole plan to her by saying she’s only playing dany and he’s all like sis same. tyrion and Varys will practically no nothing about their plans.

This is so scattered atm but bitch it’s getting written.

body:
Brienne: So, we have some news.

Jaime: We’re having another baby!

Sansa: Yayy!! Please be another girl!

Bran, to Sansa: You wanna know? I can look.

Brienne: Bran, no!

Arya: For fucks sake! Aren’t there enough kids in this family already?

Gendry: Boy or girl, I don’t care, but I’m teaching them to make swords because I can’t be the only one in this fucking family who makes the weapons. You people are killing me!

Joanna: *sobbing loudly*

Pod: *sobbing louder*

Jaime: Jo…Pod…are these happy cries?

Joanna: NO!

Pod: YES!

Jaime: Told you it was gonna be a disaster.

Brienne: Shut up! This is your fault. Seven kids? Who wants seven kids?!?

summary: She remembered a summer’s snow in Winterfell when Arya and Bran had ambushed her as she emerged from the keep one morning....
body:
She remembered a summer’s snow in Winterfell when Arya and Bran had ambushed her as she emerged from the keep one morning. They’d each had a dozen snowballs to hand, and she’d had none. Bran had been perched on the roof of the covered bridge, out of reach, but Sansa had chased Arya through the stables and around the kitchen until both of them were breathless. She might even have caught her, but she’d slipped on some ice. Her sister came back to see if she was hurt. When she said she wasn’t, Arya hit her in the face with another snowball, but Sansa grabbed her leg and pulled her down and was rubbing snow in her hair when Jory came along and pulled them apart, laughing.

- A Storm of Swords, Sansa VII

summary: Honestly, I pity Maisie too because you can feel how she started to detach herself from Arya when she slowly lost everything...
body: Honestly, I pity Maisie too because you can feel how she started to detach herself from Arya when she slowly lost everything that made her human and relatable. She’s always like “arya’s a killer and she should’ve died killing cersei and she’s asexual and a strong independent woman who don’t need no man” she’s clearly not happy with what they’ve did to Arya but she can’t say. Instead she has to cherish her ending and she will prob say shit like “yeah that was the perfect ending for arya because she’s a loner who wants to be free and away from people and she will prob die on her way to see whats west of westeros” it’s so sad. Because d&d made her lose that connection to Arya. She even disregards Arya’s intelligence a lot, always praising Sansa’s alleged intellectual superiority and emphasizing Arya’s rash, violent decision-making. It makes me so angry that she can’t even defend her character. Because she doesn’t care anymore.
